OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784823525
OL,3,CRansacked cafe owner says anti-social
OL,4,Cbehaviour ruining city centre
OL,6,FA Belfast businessman has told how a
OL,7,Fyob ransacked his city centre cafe
OL,8,Fafter smashing the window with a beer
OL,9,Fkeg and says anti-social behaviour is
OL,10,Fat "tipping point".
OL,12,FRichard Evans, owner of the Pocket
OL,13,FCafe, claimed he and others who have
OL,14,Finvested in the area are facing an
OL,15,F"untenable situation" and called for
OL,16,Faction in an open letter to Belfast
OL,17,FCity Council.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
