OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784823525
OL,3,CRansacked cafe owner says anti-social
OL,4,Cbehaviour ruining city centre
OL,6,FHe sounded the warning just weeks
OL,7,Fbefore the city is set to host Fleadh
OL,8,FCheoil na hEireann, the world's
OL,9,Fbiggest celebration of Irish music and
OL,10,Fculture, for the first time,
OL,11,Fdescribing the "deterioration of the
OL,12,Fcity centre" as a "daily reality"
OL,13,Faffecting traders, staff, residents
OL,14,Fand tourists alike.
OL,16,F"In recent months, the scale and
OL,17,Fseverity of drug-related activity in
OL,18,Fthe city centre has escalated
OL,19,Fdramatically," Mr Evans wrote.
OL,26,@pD@LrbsD@POUtD@LO]tD@SOUtD@aO]xD@AOU{D@
OL,26,ANO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
