OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784823525
OL,3,CRansacked cafe owner says anti-social
OL,4,Cbehaviour ruining city centre
OL,6,FResponding, a Belfast City Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said it is "committed to
OL,8,Fmaking our city centre the best it can
OL,9,Fbe for residents, visitors and
OL,10,Fbusinesses, and to tackling the
OL,11,Fchallenges we, like other cities, face
OL,12,Faround homelessness, addiction and
OL,13,Fanti-social behaviour".
OL,15,FThey said they have "led the way" with
OL,16,Fa multi-agency approach to support
OL,17,Fthose facing homelessness, and are
OL,18,Fengaging to look at overdose
OL,19,Fprevention facilities.
OL,26,@oD@YOUuD@VO]wD@UOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
