OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784823525
OL,3,CRansacked cafe owner says anti-social
OL,4,Cbehaviour ruining city centre
OL,6,F"Our successful bid to bring Fleadh
OL,7,FCheoil na hEireann to Belfast this
OL,8,Fsummer, as well as in 2027, is
OL,9,Fexpected to bring over 800,000
OL,10,Fvisitors into our city and generate
OL,11,Fmillions for our local economy," they
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"We have worked closely with the
OL,15,Fbusiness community to help them
OL,16,Fprepare for the event and make the
OL,17,Fmost of the opportunities it offers,
OL,18,Fand we will continue to work towards
OL,19,Fattracting more events of this calibre
OL,20,Fto our city.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@LrbsD@`O]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
