PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784823525
OL,3,CRansacked cafe owner says anti-social
OL,4,Cbehaviour ruining city centre
OL,6,F"A multi-agency approach will be in
OL,7,Fplace during the Fleadh to support
OL,8,Fbusinesses, visitors and residents,
OL,9,Fwith enhanced co-ordination between
OL,10,Forganisations, particularly in the
OL,11,Fcity centre, to deliver a safe and
OL,12,Fwelcoming event for everyone."
